channel.title: ALMOST Full 100% current RuneScape Varrock Fountain
channel.description:
Well, I removed the old fountain using SWAT's client-side remove object method(<3) but the objects are server side and the models have a few glitches(they don't have a back! D: )
But the walkway in between the fountain is 100% walkable. Here's a picture;
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/e96lag.png[/img]
I whipped this together in like... 10 minutes so I know it sucks but meh.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: June 26, 2009, 12:17:38 am[/size][hr]Pic of what it looks like in official: [IMG]http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_fCpt3eFcRGQ/Rl2JUMOY0NI/AAAAAAAAAnM/JMaPmGKFh5Q/s320/Varrock+Centre.jpg[/img]
